    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Baseline\nECG\nnormal or maybe slightly long QTc\nDuring (symptomatic) catecholaminergic episodes\nIncreased HR leads to progressive ventricular ectopy --> isolated PVCs--> bigeminy--> runs of nonsustained vtach--> sustained\nVtach\n/\npolymorphic ventricular tachycardia\nEchocardiography\nwill show normal heart",
